nodes.text: A Jawa warlord who was associated with the Jedi resided on the Outer Rim planet Tatooine. The warlord operated during the Galactic Civil War between the Galactic Empire and the Alliance to Restore the Republic. The Jawa had yellow eyes, wore brown robes attributed to the species, and used an ion blaster.

The character was depicted on the "Jawa Warlord" card for The Price of Victory, an expansion set of cards for the Star Wars Galaxies Trading Card Game. The Jawa, whose gender was unspecified, was illustrated by artist Kerem Beyit.
